name: Yamaha YZF-R1
description: The Yamaha YZF-R1 is a high-performance sport bike known for its advanced electronics, powerful 998cc engine, and exceptional handling. It features a full suite of rider aids including traction control, quick shifter, and adjustable suspension for a thrilling and precise riding experience.

name: Kawasaki Ninja ZX-6R
manufacturer: Kawasaki Heavy Industries Motorcycle & Engine Company
description: The Kawasaki Ninja ZX-6R is a sport bike that delivers a blend of performance and agility. With a 636cc inline-four engine, advanced electronics, and aggressive styling, it offers a thrilling riding experience both on the track and on the street.
